name: Super Galax-I-Birds
overview: Super Galax-I Birds is a 2019 freeware game that is somewhat only loosely based on the original Galax-i-Birds from Firebird back in 1986. Blast your way through hordes of enemy birds in this fun shoot 'em up. Developed by Jason Kelk and Andy Vaisey and first released on the CSDB on February 20, 2019.
